Rating: 3
I used 5 cloves of garlic, and switched out beans for bell peppers, but this was pretty good. And simple. Given previous reviews, I was wary of using the pasta water, but, in my case, adding it was what finally turned the sauce light and creamy. Good recipe to use up veggies in the icebox.

